<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/para/osa-csm-6) 80% 35% no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 2px #000000; padding: 8px 15px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-size:1.5em;"><strong>敏感事务办公室自动安防系统</strong></span></span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:1em;">OSA-CSM-Ⅵ型安全模因已启动。</span></p>
</div>
